          "defaultParameters": {
            "code": "# Step 2: Raw echo with noise (after LNA) — full view + adaptive-x crop in ONE\n# block, faithful (surface3d_pair_gl, NO max-pool). The crop is complex-upsampled\n# by F; its title/status note the upsample factor. Toggle Full/Crop in the plot.\nrg_axis = (t_r - t_r_center) * c / 2\n_W = float(view_scale)\n\n_rc = np.where((rg_axis >= -_W) & (rg_axis <= _W))[0]\n_ac = np.where((az_pos  >= -_W) & (az_pos  <= _W))[0]\n_sub = s_raw[_ac[0]:_ac[-1]+1, _rc[0]:_rc[-1]+1]\n_rgx = rg_axis[_rc[0]:_rc[-1]+1]; _azx = az_pos[_ac[0]:_ac[-1]+1]\nF = crop_upsample_factor(len(_azx), len(_rgx))\n_mag = upsample_complex(_sub, F)\n_rgu = upsample_axis(_rgx, F); _azu = upsample_axis(_azx, F)\n\nsurface3d_pair_gl(\n    s_raw, rg_axis, az_pos, 'Step 2: Raw echo with noise (full view)',\n    _mag, _rgu, _azu, 'Step 2: Raw echo with noise (x%d crop)' % F,\n    status_b='upsample x%d' % F)",
            "label": "Plot Raw Echo with noise",
